These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, coffee
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, rowing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
3. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage         | sprite | mirinda   | coffee |
| Sport   | rowing | parkour | soccer        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, scientific, western
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, august
1. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person who's birthday is in march##7
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
3. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | documentary   | scientific   |
| Birthday        | june | august | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, may, august
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk, mirinda
1. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
2. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person drinking soy-milk##7
3. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Birthday        | may | august | april |
| Beverage   | soy-milk       | mirinda     | milk         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, bellflower
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, soccer
1. the person who growsbellflower is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growslily##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who growslily##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Flower           | lily | bellflower | daisy |
| Sport   | soccer  | swimming | rugby    |

