.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, house
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, lemonade
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
3. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
4. the fan of hip-hop is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the fan of house##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | house | dubstep |
| Beverage           | sprite    | lemonade      | tea  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, peas, strawberry
House: townhouse, modern, cottage
1. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
2. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
3. the person eating strawberry is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
4. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Food   | peas | lemon | strawberry |
| House   | cottage        | modern   | townhouse     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, ebony, orange
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, horse
1. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the horse and the person who likes orange##2
2. the person who likes ebony is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8
3. the person who likes orange is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8
4. the owner of the horse is the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Color   | yellow | ebony | orange |
| Pet        | horse      | pony    | hedgehog |

