.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, montecristo, dunhill
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, ship, skateboard
1. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
2. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5
3. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Cigar          | dunhill | havana  | montecristo |
| Transport   | train     | ship | skateboard   |

