.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-10::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, february, march
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, taxi, helicopter
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Birthday   | february | march        | january    |
| Transport      | taxi  | helicopter | airplane |

