.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-13::.
City: san-francisco, prague, marseilles
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, camping, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
3. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |   3    |
| City   | san-francisco        | prague   | marseilles  |
| Hobby        | camping | card-games | cooking |

