.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, nectarine, apple
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, snowmobile
1. the person eating apple is not to the right of the person driving the motorbike##8
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person eating apple##1
3. the person eating apple is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating cucumber##2
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | cucumber       | apple      | nectarine |
| Transport         | car | motorbike | snowmobile     |

