3. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
5. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| City   | new-york | london | colone    |
| Beverage    | almond-milk   | iced-tea      | mirinda |

