.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-19::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, fisherman, engineer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, classical
1. the engineer is in the middle##1
2. the fan of classical is the engineer##1
3. the engineer is somewhere between the freelancer and the fisherman##7
4. the fisherman is not to the left of the fan of funk##8
5. the fan of funk is not to the left of the engineer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Job   | freelancer   | engineer    | fisherman  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | classical | funk |

