.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, red, light-blue
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, tennis
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who likes light-blue##7
2. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Color         | azure | red | light-blue |
| Sport   | tennis  | water-polo    | handball    |

 